OL,3,CAnimal ban for woman after discovery
OL,4,Cof dog resembling 'walking skeleton'
OL,6,FA woman from Canterbury in Kent has
OL,7,Fbeen banned from owning pets for five
OL,8,Fyears after puppies were found
OL,9,Femaciated and the mother dog
OL,10,Fresembling "a walking skeleton".
OL,12,FThe court heard how RSPCA Inspector
OL,13,FTina Nash visited Claire Jane
OL,14,FHodgson's home in Dorman Avenue North
OL,15,Fin Aylesham, on 3 March 2024 with a
OL,16,Fpolice officer, and found six
OL,17,Femaciated pups shut in an upstairs
OL,18,Froom and the male father had been
OL,19,Flocked in a bathroom.
