OL,6,FAll were in filthy and hazardous
OL,7,Fconditions with the puppies found
OL,8,Fscavenging for food amongst the empty
OL,9,Ffood cans and wrappers as no food was
OL,10,Favailable.
OL,12,FThe remains of a dog were also
OL,13,Fdiscovered in a bin bag outside.
OL,15,FInspector Nash said: "There was broken
OL,16,Fglass in the hallway, chocolate
OL,17,Fbiscuit wrappers and empty bottles of
OL,18,Falcohol strewn about, and a mattress
OL,19,Fon the floor.
