OL,6,F"The home was dirty, smelled strongly,
OL,7,Fand appeared not to have been cleaned
OL,8,Fin quite some time. Dog urine and
OL,9,Ffaeces were trodden into the flooring."
OL,11,FA brindle and white female dog named
OL,12,FSkylar was found in an emaciated
OL,13,Fstate. "She was like a walking
OL,14,Fskeleton," said Inspector Nash.
OL,16,F"She was subdued and growling, her
OL,17,Fbody condition was 1 out of 9. Her
OL,18,Fears were down, tail tucked, and she
OL,19,Fappeared to be living a miserable
OL,20,Fexistence."
