OL,6,FSix puppies - named White boy, Jacks,
OL,7,FElbow, Luna, White girl and Pirate -
OL,8,Fwere found shut in a room upstairs.
OL,10,F"They were all in poor condition.
OL,12,F"The room was filthy with faeces and
OL,13,Furine on the floor, and there were
OL,14,Fempty food and water bowls. The stench
OL,15,Fwas overwhelming.
OL,17,F"The pups were desperately trying to
OL,18,Feat anything; tins, wrappers, and
OL,19,Frubbish, when they left the room."
