OL,6,FWhen asked to show the dog food,
OL,7,FHodgson admitted there was none left,
OL,8,Fexplaining the dogs had eaten it all.
OL,10,FShe said the male dog had been locked
OL,11,Fin the bathroom because she was
OL,12,Fdisgusted by him after he allegedly
OL,13,Fate one of the puppies.
OL,15,FThe male dog, Hooch, was also
OL,16,Fextremely underweight and lethargic,
OL,17,Fwith bones visibly protruding.
