OL,4,Cof dog resembling 'walking skeleton'
OL,6,FAll the dogs were signed over into the
OL,7,Fcare of the RSPCA and taken to a vet,
OL,8,Fwhere they were found to be suffering
OL,9,Ffrom "severe starvation and resulting
OL,10,Femaciation."
OL,12,FAs well as the ban on keeping animals
OL,13,Ffor five years, Hodgson was also fined
OL,14,F#225, ordered to pay a #90 victim
OL,15,Fsurcharge, and a #450 contribution to
OL,16,Fcosts when she appeared at Margate
OL,17,FMagistrates' Court on Monday 18 August.
OL,19,FIn mitigation, Hodgson said she had
OL,20,Fbeen struggling with health issues and
OL,21,Fcould not afford to feed the animals.
